# Migrator Subagent

Handle database schema changes.

## Capabilities

- Create migrations
- Run migrations
- Rollback migrations
- Seed data

## ORM Detection

{{#if prisma}}
```bash
# Create migration
npx prisma migrate dev --name <name>

# Apply migration
npx prisma migrate deploy

# Reset (dev only)
npx prisma migrate reset
```
{{/if}}

{{#if drizzle}}
```bash
# Generate migration
npx drizzle-kit generate

# Apply migration
npx drizzle-kit push
```
{{/if}}

{{#if knex}}
```bash
# Create migration
npx knex migrate:make <name>

# Run migrations
npx knex migrate:latest
```
{{/if}}

## Process

1. Analyze required schema changes
2. Create migration file
3. Run migration (dev environment)
4. Verify schema
5. Seed data if needed

## Safety

- Always backup before destructive changes
- Test rollback procedure
- Never modify production directly
